---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | GoZeroShot"
  description="Privacy Policy for GoZeroShot, including what data is collected, how it is used, and how to request deletion."
>
  <main class="main legal-page">
    <section class="legal-shell">
      <a class="back-link" href="/">Back to home</a>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="effective-date">Effective date: March 23, 2026</p>

      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how GoZeroShot collects, uses, and protects
        information when you use the service.
      </p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        We may collect account information, profile information returned by
        third-party authentication providers such as TikTok, content you upload or
        schedule for publishing, and basic technical data needed to operate the
        service.
      </p>

      <h2>How we use information</h2>
      <p>
        We use collected information to authenticate users, connect third-party
        accounts, publish requested content, improve service reliability, and
        provide support.
      </p>

      <h2>TikTok data</h2>
      <p>
        If you connect your TikTok account, GoZeroShot may access profile details
        and publishing permissions that you explicitly authorize through TikTok's
        OAuth flow. We use that data only to provide login, account connection,
        and content publishing features you request.
      </p>

      <h2>Sharing of information</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell personal information. We may share information with service
        providers or platform partners only when necessary to operate the service,
        comply with law, or protect against abuse.
      </p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain information only for as long as needed to provide the service,
        maintain basic records, resolve disputes, or comply with legal obligations.
      </p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>
        You may disconnect third-party accounts at any time. You may also request
        deletion of your account data by contacting us at the email below.
      </p>

      <h2>Security</h2>
      <p>
        We use reasonable administrative and technical measures to protect data,
        but no system can guarantee absolute security.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>
        GoZeroShot is not intended for children under 13, and we do not knowingly
        collect personal information from children.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of the
        service after an update means the revised policy applies.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Privacy questions or deletion requests can be sent to
        <a href="mailto:anix@gozeroshot.dev">anix@gozeroshot.dev</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    display: block;
  }

  .legal-shell {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #4a6f98;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }

  .effective-date {
    color: #6b7280;
  }
</style>
